was published.

418
00:31:21,085 --> 00:31:22,070
Let me see it.

419
00:31:26,310 --> 00:31:28,167
It's not a flaw
to get married twice these days.

420
00:31:28,837 --> 00:31:30,505
That couple doesn't have a child.

421
00:31:30,588 --> 00:31:32,433
