You should be praising me as my senior.

440
00:32:29,653 --> 00:32:32,992
In my opinion, you're a loner
because you're neither this nor that.

441
00:32:33,075 --> 00:32:35,066
I have two kids.

442
00:32:35,149 --> 00:32:37,719
