447
00:32:54,601 --> 00:32:57,827
It's a drama. Rerun of Jung Do-jeon.

448
00:32:57,910 --> 00:33:00,047
If you want to change the world,
become powerful first.

449
00:33:00,465 --> 00:33:03,659
